ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectThe Perth Chamber of Commerce (Ontario) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the PERTH CHAMBER OF COMMERCE, in Ontario, TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from the Town of Perth to the Town of Perth, the Townships of Drummond/North Elmsley, Lanark Higlands and the Tay Valley Township.
